	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=173421><span id=Scholar>Quasare</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>44 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.96]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>The name of the robe is: Shainai's nightie (inspect my magelo).<br>You can find it on a cat girl in Shar Val named: Shainai....She is really low level and can be killed easely, just be carefull to kill her when she is far away from the guards, or they will agro...She drops the robe at each time.<br>She is roaming in the town...<br>Good luck!<br><br>ie: if you are a human bard you can see the robe on you, if you are an elf or half elf, you need an illusion mask in order to see it :)<br>check bard site: www.chez.com/legacyofaggression</p>&nbsp;<br>Valaba Noirac<br>Bard<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=150528" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=150528</a></td></td></tr>
