	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=170724><span id=Scholar>fallstarchade</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>63 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.14]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Well, depends on how you want to kite them : )<br>If you use bard kiting, you can start at 30 using fufils, but expect alot of resists still.&nbsp;&nbsp;Easier to get a group at those levels.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br>Dont make me drive by punch ye druid!<br>Longtounge Speedmyster<br>52 Bard of Xegony<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=347604" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=347604</a></td></td></tr>
