	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Sage>Slipskin</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1016 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.43]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>There are now illusion masks for almost every PC race out there (except ogre and troll).&nbsp;&nbsp;I have the dark elf (L Guk) and iksar masks (Trak's Teeth). There is a half elf mask that you can get in Jagged Pine Forest.  There is a barbarian mask you can loot in Kael Drakkel.  Most of the race mask require a good 50+ group to get.  Only the DE, Iksar and HE masks can really be acquired by a group under level 50 (only the DE mask is no drop though, I am pretty sure).</p>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></td></tr>
