	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=classes.html?class=4&mid=103529155191675>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=103529155191675>RE: Bard help</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=103529155191675#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Tue, Oct 22nd 9:18 AM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Sage>Slipskin</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1016 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.42]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>At level 5 the only instrument you need is a lute or mandolin.&nbsp;&nbsp;Either does the same job.  At level 6 get a drum.  You will eventually also need a brass instrument and a wind instrument. Each song that is not sung will need a instrument for best performance (no pun intended).  Some songs won't work at all without the correct instrument. So, you will have 4 different instruments in addition to weapons and armor to fill out your equipment needs.<br><br>Ultimately, the very best string instrument is the Lute of the Howler.  The best drum I am told is Drums of the Beast.<br><br>At level 5 the best place to level is your local newbie zone.  The best place to level varies from level to level. So, I can't really give you a better answer.  You don't mention what city your bard is in now.  Personally, I liked Greater Feydark until level 8.  Then I went by boat to East Commons and West Commons until level 17. Then I went to North Karana &amp; High Hold Pass until level 20.  Spent 2 levels in Paludal Caverns in Luclin.  Just dinged 23 in Maru Seru and Netherbian Lair last nite wtih my bard.</p>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></td></tr>
